{"tid":1804692,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"坦白講，依家真係唔係時候拍抗爭影影","createTime":"2019-12-31T07:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T02:48:41.000Z","uid":258706,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f516e1746aa79888f553c519feb879ef200895c4","tid":1804692,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"唔係反對大家對運動做紀錄後再搞相關藝術創作<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但依家真係唔係時候花錢花時間拍抗爭電影</span><br />\n對於政治運動嘅電影，唔係描述場運動贏就係輸<br />\n我哋依家贏嗱咩？輸咗咩？<br />\n我哋場運動由331第一場遊行，69大規模爆發，到依家<span style=\"color: violet;\">都仲未結束咖</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預期花時間寫劇本、徵演員同拍攝<br />\n不如花時間諗策畧應對之後點行動仲好<br />\n拍電影要用$，如期花$拍，不如攞去幫手足打官司咪仲好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">電影可以拍，<span style=\"color: gold;\">但應該喺我哋贏咗之後先至拍</span></span><br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時代革命"},{"pid":"06c122a264f5198c0a1ec4ed02a4ca368ff39e32","tid":1804692,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"Topic打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係想打&ldquo;電影&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb7a3bb408283df3e39e26d71716c6d38e1ade6","tid":1804692,"uid":305536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"德美聯署整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},{"pid":"665f1bd6508ad63b2ed43a23ac8668bc6fad4460","tid":1804692,"uid":198770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06c122a264f5198c0a1ec4ed02a4ca368ff39e32","tid":1804692,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"Topic打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係想打&ldquo;電影&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\